            "reactions" : [ ],
            "urls" : [ ],
            "text" : "I'm really excited you offered to help and that we'll get to work together!  I've been trying to get permission from Jason and Eric to send out help emails to Tucson ReactJS and Javascript but they're not responding.  I'm pretty sure Dameon will join.  My plan is to give it another week and then move forward.  Does that work for you?",
